 I intend to measure the control as sensitivity to general trends across
 countries - in the hope to identify common behaviour of consumption across
 countries and possibly comment on the factors responsible for difference
 in these trends.
 Trends such as gold consumption in India and sports expenditure in the
 U.S.
 are to be evident from this analsyis - to a sufficient accuracy to provide
 inputs to both policy and product marketing efforts.
 
\end_layout

